---
import Icon from "astro-iconify";
---
<div id="announcement-p" style="margin: 1em auto 0; padding: 0.5em; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 1px #eee; border-left: 5px; border-left: 5px solid orange; background-color: antiquewhite;">
    <div style="display:flex; margin-bottom: 0.5em; width: 100%;">
        <h2>📣 Announcement</h2>
        <label style="text-decoration:underline; cursor:pointer;" onclick="document.querySelector('#announcement-p').style.display = 'none'">
            <Icon name="mdi:close" />
        </label>
    </div>
    <p style="padding: 0.5em">
        We started the move to a <a target="_blank" href="https://cozy-reader.vercel.app">new address</a>. If you don't mind losing your current history, you can just use the new environment as usual. Let us know if you have data you want moved over by <a href="https://ayco.io/gh/cozy/issues/new">filing an issue</a>. Thank you for your patience and understanding. 🙏
    </p>
</div>

<style>
    h2, svg {
        flex: 1;
    }
    svg {
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        cursor: pointer;
        border: 1px solid #ccc
    }
</style>
